    WHERE [t].[UserId] = @__request_UserId_0
    ORDER BY [t].[Date] DESC, [t].[CreatedAt] DESC
    OFFSET @__p_1 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_2 ROWS ONLY

    WHERE [t].[UserId] = @__request_UserId_0 AND [t].[Date] >= @__request_Filter_StartDate_Value_1 AND [t].[Date] <= @__request_Filter_EndDate_Value_2
    ORDER BY [t].[Date] DESC, [t].[CreatedAt] DESC
    OFFSET @__p_3 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_4 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t0]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [t0].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
ORDER BY [t0].[Date] DESC, [t0].[CreatedAt] DESC

    SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Amount], [t].[CategoryId], [t].[CreatedAt], [t].[Date], [t].[Description], [t].[Type], [t].[UpdatedAt]

    WHERE [t].[UserId] = @__request_UserId_0

    SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Amount], [t].[CategoryId], [t].[CreatedAt], [t].[Date], [t].[Description], [t].[Type], [t].[UpdatedAt]
    FROM [Transactions] AS [t]
    WHERE [t].[UserId] = @__request_UserId_0
    ORDER BY [t].[Date] DESC, [t].[CreatedAt] DESC
    OFFSET @__p_1 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_2 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t0]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [t0].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
ORDER BY [t0].[Date] DESC, [t0].[CreatedAt] DESC

2025-08-06 02:27:17.445 +03:00 [INF] Executed action FinanceTracker.API.Controllers.CategoriesController.GetCategories (FinanceTracker.API) in 6.4482ms
2025-08-06 02:27:17.446 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (2ms) [Parameters=[@__request_UserId_0='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_1='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_2='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [t0].[Id], [t0].[Amount], [t0].[Description], [t0].[Date], [t0].[Type], [t0].[CategoryId], [c].[Name] AS [CategoryName], [c].[Color] AS [CategoryColor], [t0].[CreatedAt], [t0].[UpdatedAt]
FROM (
    SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Amount], [t].[CategoryId], [t].[CreatedAt], [t].[Date], [t].[Description], [t].[Type], [t].[UpdatedAt]
    FROM [Transactions] AS [t]
    WHERE [t].[UserId] = @__request_UserId_0
    ORDER BY [t].[Date] DESC, [t].[CreatedAt] DESC
    OFFSET @__p_1 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_2 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t0]

    SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Amount], [t].[CategoryId], [t].[CreatedAt], [t].[Date], [t].[Description], [t].[Type], [t].[UpdatedAt]
    FROM [Transactions] AS [t]
    WHERE [t].[UserId] = @__request_UserId_0
    ORDER BY [t].[Date] DESC, [t].[CreatedAt] DESC
    OFFSET @__p_1 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_2 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t0]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [t0].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
ORDER BY [t0].[Date] DESC, [t0].[CreatedAt] DESC

    SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Amount], [t].[CategoryId], [t].[CreatedAt], [t].[Date], [t].[Description], [t].[Type], [t].[UpdatedAt]
    FROM [Transactions] AS [t]
    WHERE [t].[UserId] = @__request_UserId_0
    ORDER BY [t].[Date] DESC, [t].[CreatedAt] DESC
    OFFSET @__p_1 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_2 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t0]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [t0].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
ORDER BY [t0].[Date] DESC, [t0].[CreatedAt] DESC
